curricular_rows.text:
Methods and tools for assessing the coping capacity of people, 
organizations and systems, and the dimensions, including: governance; 
intelligence systems; functional capacity of health and emergency 
services; surge capacity workforce; information sharing mechanisms; 
community capacities; financial resources, including contingency 
funding; and mechanisms for emergency deployment

